{"tid":1321192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊仲有大量抗爭，但記住，唔可以有人死","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:47:12.000Z","uid":42149,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cc15cc3f6cdbae9aaaaf0f2a0f64693b2bf465","tid":1321192,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實今次好明顯係政府同市民對賭。賭注係香港人既性命。<br />\n原因好簡單，今朝有警太家屬打上電台phone in, 香港政府係等緊一個警察死，然後就可以名正言順咁開槍，甚至宵禁。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，抗爭可以，但唔可以有狗死！</span></span><br />\n而當警察因為驅趕示威者而死，成個運動真係可以停。之前既義士既犧牲就白廢。<br />\n可以好似沙田咁，但唔可以死警犬。"},{"pid":"e29409df701bc9cfa7147484e5a3c7f3659819a6","tid":1321192,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"584b2cf110a950eae7ba7569910252ee7908410a","tid":1321192,"uid":261043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"綁上鐵馬做盾牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b2b467d0c690a5e5b1f0c1fa6c0bd4917d7645","tid":1321192,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8689ce69772e632bc2e725e16cf8d5f4f91cfaa3","tid":1321192,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit